{"tid":2161193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【官方認證】黨校前教授批習遭開除黨籍 「與這個黑幫一樣的政黨徹底脫鈎了」","createTime":"2020-08-17T12:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T13:02:26.000Z","uid":36494,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6663ccd1ebb0fd085c9836461189526469cb945d","tid":2161193,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"據悉已移居美國的<span class=\"red\">中共中央黨校前教授蔡霞</span>，有傳她早前在一個紅二代秘密聚會中，狠批中共總書記習近平有如黑幫老大，又指中共如同「政治殭屍」，中共中央黨校今日公佈，蔡霞發表有嚴重政治問題和損害國家聲譽的言論，當局決定開除其黨籍，並取消她所享受的相關退休待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡霞在發言中形容中共實際上已經是「政治殭屍」，在十八屆三中全會前的兩天，搶着拋出取消國家主席任期制的說法。<span class=\"red\">她又批評，習近平完全成了一個「黑幫老大」，隨意定罪：「不支持實體經濟，就成了罪名，然後妄議中央，就成了個罪名，對黨不老實，這也叫罪名」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200817/46QQRMCJEJBILDSDZ67GHGYC2U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200817%2F46QQRMCJEJBILDSDZ67GHGYC2U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21BckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=349c26aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200817%2F46QQRMCJEJBILDSDZ67GHGYC2U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=55396931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200817/46QQRMCJEJBILDSDZ67GHGYC2U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"0527bcb2c0910477a5803c328887c9dd29a7aed3","tid":2161193,"uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">她又指，「港版國安法」表面是為了維護中共專制統治而強暴香港人民，但實質是中共在威脅全球秩序和人類文明價值，</span>從這個角度看，中共與全球為敵，尤其與人類文明為敵。"},{